PathOfBuilding.Notes:
Hey all! ^x70FF70Ronarray^7 here and this is ^x70FF70^7my ^x70FF70^xD02090Dark Pact Pathfinder Build^7! If you like the guide please make sure to Like the video as well - subscribe to the ^xE05030YouTube channel^7 for more content too! If you have questions or want to discuss anything build related - feel free to hit me on twitch or discord, I will be glad to help.
^x70FF70 Discord^7 https://discord.gg/xDQVEQahMT
^x70FF70Twitch^7 https://www.twitch.tv/ronarray
^x70FF70YouTube^7 https://www.youtube.com/@ronarray
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| ^xE05030 ^x70FF70 FAQ ^7|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|^7^7
^x70FF701.^7^xE05030 Dissolution of the Flesh^7 + ^xE05030Rathpin Globe^7 Shield are^xFFFF77 build enabling^7 ^xAF6025Uniques^7. You will need them both before fully respecking into the build.
^x70FF702.^7 ^x8888FFFlasks^7 are mandatory for the setup so make sure you have the good ones and they all have quality / good buffs.
^x70FF703.^7 It is reccommended to use ^x7070FFConcentrated Effect^7 for ^xE05030Uber bosses^7 to reach ^xFFFF77top DPS^7 and ^x7070FFAwakened Increased Area of effect^7 for ^xFFFF77comfort mapping^7. Just swap the gems depending on what you are donig. Both of them are ^x7070FFBlue^7 so it should be easy.
^xAF6025 ^x70FF704.^7 ^xAF6025^xAF6025^7It is pretty important to reach ^x70FF70Poison^7 /^xE05030 Bleed^7 / ^xD02090Corrupted Blood^7 avoidance since the build can suffer from Damage Over Time which can stop health reservation from resetting. We are reaching it through Tolerance Nodes / Protection mastery / Evasion Mastery in the Tree + Eater of Worlds implicit on boots for Bleed + 1 Corrupted jewel for poison. ^7 ^x70FF705.^7 ^x8888FF^7^xE05030Pain Attunment^7 is taken to compensate in case if the^xE05030 Life Recharge^7 ^xAF6025^7is stopped and we are dropping to low life. It also helps for the boss dps when our cast speed rises too high to stay over half health consistantly.^7 ^7 ^x70FF706.^7 ^x7070FFShock Immunity^7 should come from the Flask with T1 "of the Heron" Suffix.
^x70FF707.^7 ^xD02090Warlock^7^xFFFF77 Wildwood Ascendancy^7 is required to get ^xD02090Crimson Power^7 and stack ^xE05030Health^7 trough ^x7070FFEnergy shield^7 on armor. Get it ASAP.
^x70FF708.^7^7 You can buy diferrent corpses to use ^xE05030Ravenous^7 with. Most of the Uber Bosses are eldritch so Eldritch corpses are mandatory. ^xE05030Ravenous^7 should be reused everytime when you enter the map - it grants 15% more DPS and 15 less DMg taken.
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| ^xE05030 ^x70FF70 List of Tips and Items^7 ^7 |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
^x70FF701.^7 The ^xFFFF77^xAF6025unqiues^7 you will need in the order of importance:^7
^xAF6025 Rathpin Globe ^7/^7 ^xAF6025Dissolution of the Flesh^7 /^7^7 ^xAF6025Divinarius Imperial Skean ^7/^7 ^7^xAF6025Eyes of the Greatwolf
^x70FF702. ^7On your Rares just aim for maximum ^x7070FFEnergy Shield^7 possible and look for some ^x7070FFEnergy Shield Recharge Rate^7 if possible.
^x70FF703.^7 ^xAF6025That Which Was Taken Unique Jewel ^x70FF70^7- could be a great way to recieve Frenzy Charges and culling strike source, so try to get a good one. ^7 ^x70FF704.^7 Make sure that you have ^x7070FFZealotry^7 together with^xE05030 Divine Blessing ^7to avoid reservation. ^7 |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|^7 ^x70FF70 Thank you for checking the build out! ^7 ^x70FF70Please like the video and subscribe to the channel if you enjoyed it.^7 |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| ^x70FF70
